reports/deep_acceptance/visual_acceptance_report_20260422_221125.html:704:                <div class="caption">Williamson 1996 对比图把 Cd、Cl_rms、wake centerline deficit 与 Strouhal 放在一张科研表板里，突出“数值正确”与“方法仍需修补”同时成立。</div>
