     1	# CFD Harness UI — Frontend (Phase 0)
     2	
     3	Vite + React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS. Implements Screen 4
     4	(Validation Report) from `docs/ui_design.md` and is the starting
     5	surface for the Path-B Agentic V&V Workbench (DEC-V61-002).
     6	
     7	## Quick start
     8	
     9	```bash
    10	# 1. Start the FastAPI backend in another shell (loopback only):
    11	uvicorn ui.backend.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000 --reload
    12	
    13	# 2. Install + run the dev server:
    14	cd ui/frontend
    15	pnpm install        # or: npm install
    16	pnpm dev            # or: npm run dev
    17	```
    18	
    19	Dev server binds to `127.0.0.1:5173` and proxies `/api/**` to the
    20	backend on `127.0.0.1:8000`. Nothing listens on a public interface
    21	in Phase 0.
    22	
    23	## Phase-0 scope
    24	
    25	- `GET /api/cases` — renders the whitelist-of-10 with contract chips.
    26	- `GET /api/validation-report/{case_id}` — renders Screen 4 against
    27	  the three canonical cases (`differential_heated_cavity`,
    28	  `circular_cylinder_wake`, `turbulent_flat_plate`). Other cases
    29	  still load; their contract status will say `UNKNOWN` until a
    30	  measurement fixture lands.
    31	
    32	Out of scope for Phase 0: case editing, run control, audit-package
    33	export, authentication, dashboards. See `docs/ui_roadmap.md`.
    34	
    35	## Design tokens
    36	
    37	All design tokens live in `tailwind.config.ts` (palette, fonts,
    38	contract-status colors). If you want to bump a token, edit it there
    39	once and rebuild — do not hard-code hex values in components.
    40	
    41	## Component inventory (Phase 0)
    42	
    43	| Component                     | Purpose                                        |
    44	| ----------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
    45	| `Layout`                      | Left nav + main content shell (dark surface)   |
    46	| `PassFailChip`                | Three-state contract chip (PASS/HAZARD/FAIL)   |
    47	| `BandChart`                   | Inline-SVG tolerance-band chart (no Plotly)    |
    48	| `AuditConcernList`            | Per-concern rows with collapsible detail       |
    49	| `PreconditionList`            | Physics preconditions with satisfied/unmet     |
    50	| `DecisionsTrail`              | DEC-xxx linked list with autonomy marker       |
    51	| `CaseListPage`                | Index route (`/cases`)                         |
    52	| `ValidationReportPage`        | Screen 4 (`/cases/:caseId/report`)             |
    53	
    54	## Typecheck / build
    55	
    56	```bash
    57	pnpm typecheck
    58	pnpm build
    59	```
    60	
    61	`pnpm build` runs `tsc -b` first, so a type error breaks the build.
    62	
    63	## Not covered yet
    64	
    65	- Unit tests for the React components (Phase 1 — we'll add Vitest
    66	  + Testing Library then).
    67	- Storybook / visual regression (Phase 4 Dashboard).
    68	- i18n (Phase 6 Enterprise).
    69	
    70	---
    71	
    72	Path B workbench · Phase 0 · DEC-V61-002.

