    22	      evidence_ref: "src/foam_agent_adapter.py:1178-1184 — nu=1/Re=1/7600 with U_bulk=1. Regime argument documented in yaml header lines 6-13; accepted under Gate Q-4 Path A. The regime match is qualitative-plateau, not a 2% quantified tolerance."
