    82	                               │
    83	                               ▼
    84	                         ui/frontend  /learn  /pro
    85	```
    86	
    87	- `MockExecutor`: unit-test fast path; returns preset results.
    88	- `FoamAgentExecutor`: the real Docker + OpenFOAM path (optional,
    89	  install via `.venv/bin/pip install -e '.[cfd-real-solver]'`).
    90	- `src/convergence_attestor.py` + `src/comparator_gates.py`: the A1..A6 /
    91	  G1..G5 hard-FAIL guards that stop a PASS-washed verdict from leaking out
