plane_channel_flow => INCOMPATIBLE_WITH_LITERATURE_DISGUISED_AS_COMPATIBLE | INCOMPATIBLE_WITH_LITERATURE_DISGUISED_AS_COMPATIBLE — laminar icoFoam at Re_bulk=5600 cannot reproduce Kim 1987 / Moser 1999 Re_τ=180 turbulent DNS u+ profile. ATTEST_PASS is a comparator-path artifact; a physics-honest verdict is FAIL. No comparator or extractor fix can bridge the gap — this is a solver-choice incompatibility. Queued for Phase 9 real-solver routing (either move to pimpleFoam + LES, or demote the case to laminar Poiseuille benchmark at a new gold).
impinging_jet => INCOMPATIBLE_WITH_LITERATURE_DISGUISED_AS_COMPATIBLE | INCOMPATIBLE_WITH_LITERATURE_DISGUISED_AS_COMPATIBLE — two independent physics hazards compound: (1) adapter produces a 2D planar slice, not an axisymmetric wedge; (2) ATTEST_FAIL at A4 (p_rgh iteration cap) means no converged steady field exists for Nu extraction. Prior fixture reported ref_value=0.0042 which is dimensionally Cf, not Nusselt — pure value-leakage into the wrong observable. A PASS on this case today is vacuous; queued for Phase 9 axisymmetric-wedge mesh + buoyantFoam solver-config audit.
naca0012_airfoil => PARTIALLY_COMPATIBLE | PARTIALLY_COMPATIBLE — physics preconditions #1 and #2 satisfied, precondition #3 not satisfiable under the current extraction scheme. Deviation is quantifiable, direction is known, and the 20% tolerance + PASS_WITH_DEVIATIONS pattern encodes this. No false-PASS risk.
rayleigh_benard_convection => COMPATIBLE | COMPATIBLE — all preconditions satisfied at Ra=1e6. NOT transferable to Ra≥1e9 without mesh refinement (see differential_heated_cavity physics_contract for the high-Ra regime).

